message.body: Babe! Check your messages! Your car was hurted last night :(.
How's it going babe? I'm thinking of you. You need me? Anything I can do?

I'm alright. There wasn't really anything to. Already had a police report filed. Usaa is handling it. Repair shop will call tomorrow. Eric said it will be close on whether it's totalled or not. It's only one panel, but it's one that isn't removable
Fine! Almost home. How are you sweet thing?
At my desk. Eating chicken rice soup and saltines and sweating a lot. Feeling yicky.
Aww babe, I thought you were at home! What are you doing at work? I don't want you to get worse!
I have that thing with my mentor. All went well?
Yeah. It went well, she cracked me all over! Work soon :(
